<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello {{customerName}},</h1>
        <p>You have been added as a guest to the following event:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Event Name: {{eventName}}</li>
            <li>Date: {{eventDate}}</li>
            <li>Location: {{eventLocation}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please confirm your attendance by clicking the link below:</p>
        <a href="{{confirmationLink}}">Confirm Attendance</a>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Your Event Organizer</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>